I don't think I can.

259
00:19:07,187 --> 00:19:10,691
No one wants you back together
more than I do, but I'm her best friend.

260
00:19:10,774 --> 00:19:12,192
I can't start spying on her, can I?

261
00:19:48,770 --> 00:19:50,480
-Been a while.
-Good to see you.

262
00:19:52,024 --> 00:19:53,358
Just tell me, already.

263
00:19:54,818 --> 00:19:56,445
Tell you what?

264
00:19:56,528 --> 00:19:58,197
We both know you have a secret.

265
00:19:59,489 --> 00:20:00,908
